      "rationale": "The validation activity used production-equivalent 7.5 mm non-cannulated screws in the ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration, which is the same geometry and loading mode as the COU. Minor differences in vertebral body surrogate stiffness between the two laboratories were documented and assessed as having negligible impact on QoI predictions."
